<section class="container story " role="main">
<div id="story-header"
>
<h1 class="heading section-main-heading link">
<a href="http://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/">
Columns & Blogs
</a>
</h1>
<p
class="published-date">
April 18, 2014 8:40 PM
</p>
<h1
class="title">
Charlotte Bobcats&rsquo; Chris Douglas-Roberts: Perseverance, hard work fueled long NBA journey
</h1>
</div>
<div class="row
story-rail-wrapper">
<div class="wide-rail">
<div class="toplines">
Most of us are not like the Miami Heat’s LeBron James. ... Most of us are more like Charlotte Bobcats’ guard-forward Chris Douglas-Roberts. At least, we’d like to be.
</div>
<div class="story-gallery ">
</div>
<div id="story-body-items"
>
<div
class="byline element-spacing-small">
By Tom Sorensen - <a href="mailto:tsorensen@charlotteobserver.com">tsorensen@charlotteobserver.com</a>
</div>
<div class="share-tools-wrapper">
<!--
Widget ID: Feature Master with title feature master share buttons:
Referenced feature mi.masterConfig.shareButtons, which was empty. Attempting fall-back value.
-->
<ul class="share-icons">
