<div class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></div>
</li>
<li class="more" onClick="return true">
<ul class="share-options">
<li class="linked-in"><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3a%2f%2fwww.charlotteobserver.com%2fsports%2fspt-columns-blogs%2farticle9114314.html&title=Charlotte+Bobcats%e2%80%99+Chris+Douglas-Roberts%3a+Perseverance%2c+hard+work+fueled+long+NBA+journey"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-linkedin"></span>LinkedIn</a></li>
<li class="google"><a title="Share on Google Plus" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3a%2f%2fwww.charlotteobserver.com%2fsports%2fspt-columns-blogs%2farticle9114314.html" onclick="window.open(this.href, '', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=400,width=600');return false;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-google-plus"></span>Google+</a></li>
<li class="pinterest"><a href="http://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3a%2f%2fwww.charlotteobserver.com%2fsports%2fspt-columns-blogs%2farticle9114314.html&description=Charlotte+Bobcats%e2%80%99+Chris+Douglas-Roberts%3a+Perseverance%2c+hard+work+fueled+long+NBA+journey&media=http%3a%2f%2fwww.charlotteobserver.com%2fstatic%2fimages%2fcharlotteobserver%2ffacebook.jpg"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pinterest-p"></span>Pinterest</a></li>
<li class="reddit"><a href="http://www.reddit.com/submit?url=http://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/article9114314.html"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-reddit"></span>Reddit</a></li>
<li class="print"><a href="javascript:window.print();"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-print"></span>Print</a></li>
